@node "TB303" "TB303"

@{JCENTER}@{b}@{u}TB303@{ub}@{uu}

I'm most proud of this baby. This is a very good machine & I totally adore the 
sound of it. If I hear the sound of this one, from the low & pumping sound,
to the high & bleeping tunes, it'll make my day completely.

@endnode
@node "TR808" "TR808"

@{JCENTER}@{b}@{u}TR808@{ub}@{uu}

 Great sounds. Look pretty too. Nice and Black, with some beautiful buttons ;) 
 Good for making @{b}REAL@{ub} underground Acid, Electro and Techno.


@endnode
@node "TR909" "TR909"

@{JCENTER}@{b}@{u}TR909@{ub}@{uu}

The sounds that this machine can produce, are so f**king hard, you won't believe it. 
Very good for making Hardcore, HardAcid, Techno and a lot more....


@endnode
@node "TR707" "TR707"

@{JCENTER}@{b}@{u}TR707@{ub}@{uu}

Great machine for making Acid-House, but some of the sounds are a bit weak :-( 
Also good to sync a TB303.

@endnode
@node "TR606" "TR606"

@{JCENTER}@{b}@{u}TR606@{ub}@{uu}

What can I say 'bout this one. Small in size and sound. Fits with the TB303. 
Maybye a bit under-rated. Good for making Acid and Electro music.

@endnode
